eu.itesla_project.iidm.network

Interface GeneratorAdder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdentifiableAdder<GeneratorAdder>, SingleTerminalConnectableAdder<GeneratorAdder>

    public interface GeneratorAdder
extends SingleTerminalConnectableAdder<GeneratorAdder>
    To create a generator, from a VoltageLevel instance call the VoltageLevel.newGenerator() method to get a generator builder instance.

    Example: 

        VoltageLevel vl = ...
    Generator g = vl.newGenerator()
            .setId("g1")
            ...
        .add();
    Author:
    Geoffroy Jamgotchian
    See Also:
    Generator, VoltageLevel
